*'' Petrolia: The Landscape of America's First Oil Boom ''(Johns Hopkins, 2003; {{ISBN|0801877326}}, {{ISBN|978-0801877322}})<ref>{{jstor|3594746}}; {{jstor|3985468}}; {{jstor|25147879}}; {{doi|10.1086/533300}}</ref>
*'' Crude Reality: Petroleum in World History'' (Rowman & Littlefield, 2012, {{ISBN|0742556549}}, {{ISBN|978-0742556546}}), selected as a [[Outstanding Academic Title|CHOICE outstanding academic book]] for 2012
He is the editor of:
*'' Climate Change: An Encyclopedia of History and Science '' (4 vols, {{ISBN|1598847619}}, {{ISBN|978-1598847611}})

